{"tid":2189921,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"30歲或以上仲未做到公司中/高層嘅廢男，千祈咪揀","createTime":"2020-09-05T08:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T09:19:40.000Z","uid":29540,"like":10,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1281816c8cee3ae56937b7e5c68510533db008d5","tid":2189921,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:37:41.000Z","msg":"一個人正常21/22歲左右大學畢業，然後做幾年嘢有一定經驗同人脈之後升做企業嘅中高層根本好正常。<br />\n所以如果一個男人去到30歲仲係做緊基層。我敢講佢一定係一件人形垃圾。<br />\n女人最怕嫁錯郎，如果你身邊嘅男人廿到尾就黎三十都仲係冇乜成就的話。聽我講，拋棄佢搵過第二個，揀男人就好似玩股票一樣，要識止蝕離場同時揀有潛力的股。"},{"pid":"aba831dfc52c468982d082a2ce2239893d0f49e2","tid":2189921,"uid":49119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"某程度上都同意"},{"pid":"20d1d96431228c1b2f6c8e5f27109f4d34eee0c8","tid":2189921,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:39:58.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"752ff3d1f0215094e94974cda2727670cd753b1b","tid":2189921,"uid":297546,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:42:30.000Z","msg":"如果職業係兒子呢？"},{"pid":"91915b231588bf66d9512ead206a6fbf543c88ab","tid":2189921,"uid":48109,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:44:21.000Z","msg":"調返轉睇，30歲做高層有成就做咩要㨂你？"},{"pid":"fff8d5866ebb50c7e39dc92988351c886d0055e0","tid":2189921,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:45:21.000Z","msg":"其實我對三十而立呢句說話有d保留<br />\n<br />\n做幾年野之後去讀master洗底入ibank 做analyst grade點睇？低層但係五皮一個月"},{"pid":"0048e4c403b8c08e812cc9fd245fcddb411ce922","tid":2189921,"uid":55010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:54:02.000Z","msg":"打機咁有流程😂😂😂"},{"pid":"afd9479410251cc2bb659c4ad517e30f0d0e42d7","tid":2189921,"uid":91791,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fff8d5866ebb50c7e39dc92988351c886d0055e0","tid":2189921,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:45:21.000Z","msg":"其實我對三十而立呢句說話有d保留<br />\n<br 